flowchart TD
    A[Start: Packet Processing Need] --> B{Cross-platform required?}
    B -->|Yes| C[Use libpcap]
    B -->|No| D{Need to modify or drop packets?}
    D -->|Yes| E[Use eBPF/XDP]
    D -->|No| F{Traffic > 1M PPS?}
    F -->|Yes| E
    F -->|No| G{Quick prototype or one-off tool?}
    G -->|Yes| C
    G -->|No| H{Need stateful kernel logic?}
    H -->|Yes| E
    H -->|No| I{Team familiar with eBPF?}
    I -->|Yes| J[Either works: prefer simpler]
    I -->|No| C

    C --> K[libpcap Path]
    E --> L[eBPF/XDP Path]
    J --> M[Evaluate specific requirements]
